of Pied Wagtails Motacilla alba in Israel and abroad. Sandgrouse 13:49-53.
5. Leshem, Y., and Y. Yom-Tov (1996). The
magnitude and timing of migration by soaring
raptors and storks over Israel. Ibis 138:188-203.
6. Markovets, M., and R. Yosef (2005). Phenology,
duration and site fidelity of wintering
Bluethroat (Luscinia svecica) at Eilat, Israel. J. Arid Environ. 61:93-100.
