15. Yosef, R., L. Fornasari, P. Tryjanowski, M.
Bechard, G. Kaltenecker, and K. L. Bildstein
(2003). Differential spring migration of adult
and juvenile Levant Sparrowhawk Accipiter
brevipes through Eilat, Israel. J. Raptor Res. 37:31-36.
16. Yosef, R., and L. Fornasari
(2004). Simultaneous decline in Steppe
Eagle(Aquila nipalensis) populations and Levant
Sparrowhawk (Accipiter brevipes) reproductive
success: coincidence or a Chernobyl legacy? Ostrich 75:20-24.
17. Yosef, R., and N. Chernetsov
(2004). Stopover ecology of migratory Sedge
Warblers (Acrocephalus schoenobaenus) at Eilat, Israel. Ostrich 75:52-56.
18. Yosef, R., and N. Chernetsov (2005). Longer
is fatter: body mass changes of migrant Reed
Warblers (Acrocephalus scirpaceus) staging at
